Investec Asset Management is a specialist provider of active investment products.
We provide services to institutional and individual investors. Our range of asset management investment capabilities is intentionally innovative.
With strong roots in Africa, Investec Asset Management have:

Gained expertise in frontier markets and commodity investment.
Established presence in the United Kingdom.
Gained a perfect vantage point for global investing.
Built investment capabilities in areas where we have proven expertise.
Seamlessly integrated our asset management processes within a tight risk management framework.

We own each investment capability and continually strive to improve and develop these over the longer term.










