Corporate Debt and Equity





Growth & Acquisition Finance




Corporate & Acquisition Finance




Growth & Acquisition Finance
We work with entrepreneurs, management teams and private equity houses to provide finance to UK mid-market companies. We offer revolving and amortising senior cash flow lending, mezzanine finance and minority equity on either a standalone or integrated basis. Our flexible solutions cover the entire capital structure and range between £5 million to £50 million+.
 
Corporate & Acquisition Finance

We originate, structure and provide capital solutions to mid-market private equity and corporate clients based in the UK or Eurozone with an EBITDA greater than £15m. We seek to lead deals for clients with a focus on underwriting and arranging senior secured debt solutions.





