Asset Management


























About Investec Asset Management
Investec Asset Management is a specialist provider of active investment products and services to institutional and individual investors. Established in South Africa in 1991, the firm has been built from  a small start-up into an international business.
 
Our range of investment capabilities is intentionally innovative. Roots in Africa have given us expertise in frontier markets and commodity investment, while our established presence in the United Kingdom provides us with a perfect vantage point for global investing. We build investment capabilities in areas where we have proven expertise, seamlessly integrating our investment management processes within a tight risk management framework.  We truly own each investment capability and continue to improve and develop them over the longer term.
More on Asset Management





















































