Investing


























Our wealth management and investment services are entirely built around your needs.

Whether you are a private individual, charity, financial mutual, trust, or a professional advising your own clients, we are committed to understanding your goals and helping you reach them with our forward-thinking investment process.

We work hard to form enduring relationships of trust with our clients and pride ourselves on delivering service that’s second to none.

















Investment Management for Financial Advisers

Our Investment Management Services have been specifically designed to work in partnership with financial advisers and their clients.










Financial Advisers



























Investment Management for Private Clients

Our investment management solutions are built around your financial goals.










Investment Management



































Charity Services
We specialise in Charities investment management and support trustees and senior managers with ongoing training and informative seminars.
Charity Services



























Financial Planning
We offer financial planning solutions including general financial advice, retirement planning and SIPPs, estate planning and succession planning.










Financial Planning


































Court of Protection
We specialise in investing damages and compensation payments from personal injury or clinical negligence claims.

Court of Protection



























Financial Mutuals

Our expert team specialises in providing bespoke investment management solutions for financial mutuals and friendly societies.
Financial Mutuals



































Offshore Custody and Nominee Services

Our specialist team offers a bespoke service for international clients, managing investments across multiple currencies and markets.

Offshore Custody/Nominee



























Structured Products
Plans designed to complement traditional investment alternatives, distributed exclusively through financial advisers.
Structured Products


































Asset Management

Investec Asset Management is a specialist investment manager, providing a premier range of products to institutional and individual investors.

Asset Management
































